msgid ""
"If the billing address is empty and PayPal provides a shipping address, the "
"order will use the shipping address as the billing address."
msgstr ""
"Hvis faktureringsadressen er tom og PayPal oppgir en leveringsadresse, vil "
"bestillingen bruke leveringsadressen som faktureringsadresse."

