msgid ""
"Include all line item details in the payment request to PayPal so that they "
"can be seen from the PayPal transaction details page."
msgstr ""
"Inkluder alle linjeelementsdetaljer i betalingsforespørselen til PayPal slik"
" at de kan sees fra PayPal-transaksjonssiden."

